<div class="row mb-3">
  <div class="col-12">
    <p class="text-uppercase text-muted small mb-1">Projects</p>
    <h1 class="h3 mb-0">Create a new project</h1>
  </div>
</div>

<div class="row">
  <div class="col-lg-8">
    <div class="card">
      <div class="card-body">
        <%= erb :"projects/_form", locals: { project: @project, form_action: "/projects", http_method: "post", submit_label: "Create project" } %>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
  <div class="col-lg-4">
    <div class="card h-100">
      <div class="card-body">
        <h2 class="h6">Tips</h2>
        <p class="text-muted mb-0">このフォームはCSRFトークンとHTTPメソッド上書きを使用し、実運用に近いCRUDフローを再現しています。</p>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</div>
